<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3342235>
    dc:description "FIGURE 37. Holothuria (Vaneyothuria) lentiginosa lentiginosa Marenzeller, 1892 (DBUA-ECH 388: A–E). Dorsal view (A, C); ventral view (B, D); specimen, when alive (C, D); ossicles (E); holothurians most likely belonging to H. lentiginosa in situ in Azores (EMEPC–LUSO, 37°43'15\"N, 25°48'24\"W, 2009.10.08, 316 m: F) and Gorringe Bank (EMEPC–LUSO, 36°42'46\"N, 11°10'02\"W, 2009.09.13, 145 m: G)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3342235/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3342233>
    dc:description "FIGURE 36. Holothuria (Platyperona) sanctori Delle Chiaje, 1823 (DBUA-ECH 320: A, B, E; DBUA-ECH 402: C; DBUA- ECH 405: D; DBUA-ECH 398: E). Dorsal view (A, C); ventral view (B); specimen, when alive (D); ossicles (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3342233/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

